nes.apple.com/album/love-single/id328941719|dead-url=no}}</ref>而他作为独唱歌手获得钢钒认可，是在同[[B.o.B|B.o.B]]合作“Nothin' on You”以及同崔维·麦考伊合作“Billionaire”后；两首曲子在全球的多个排行榜中都跻身前十。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=B.o.B+feat.+Bruno+Mars&titel=Nothin'+On+You&cat=s|title=B.o.B feat. Bruno Mars - Nothin' on You (song)|publisher=australian-charts.com. Hung Medien|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227132540/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=B.o.B%20feat.%20Bruno%20Mars&titel=Nothin%27%20On%20You&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Travie+McCoy+feat.+Bruno+Mars&titel=Billionaire&cat=s|title=Travie McCoy feat. Bruno Mars - Billionaire (song)|publisher=australian-charts.com. Hung Medien|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130044651/https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Travie%20McCoy%20feat.%20Bruno%20Mars&titel=Billionaire&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/artist/_/BRUNO%20MARS/|title=Bruno Mars: Top 75 Releases|publisher=[[官方榜单公司|The Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-date=2011-12-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111228154011/http://www.theofficialcharts.com/artist/_/bruno%20mars|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="weeklychart">{{Cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/#/column/chartbeat/weekly-chart-notes-p-nk-bruno-mars-band-1004133464.story|title=Weekly Chart Notes: P!nk, Bruno Mars, Band Perry|date=2010-12-02|first=Gary|last=Trust|work=《[[告示牌_(雜志)|告示牌]]》|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2011-02-03|archive-date=2011-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110729050908/http://www.billboard.com/#/column/chartbeat/weekly-chart-notes-p-nk-bruno-mars-band-1004133464.story|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此之后，2010年5月11日，马尔斯又发布了名为《It's Better If You Don't Understand》（你最好不懂